The FCC entry also covers the [[SparkLAN WPEA-352ACNRBI]] which is an industrial grade version with a QCA9890-BR4B chip.
===Specifications=== :‧ Standard: 802.11ac/a/b/g/n :‧ Host interface: Mini PCI-E :‧ Chipset: [[Qualcomm Atheros]] QCA9880-BR4A :‧ Antenna: 3 x IPEX connectors, 3T3R :‧ Data rate up to 1.3Gbps :‧ Enhanced wireless security: WEP, WPA, WPA2, 802.1x :‧ Support Linux
